Text:
Drop the key (.ini) and WindowsDoctor (.exe) files from the Crk folder into the: 

C:Program Files (x86)Windows Doctor >folder. 64Bit
or 
C:Program FilesWindows Doctor >folder.  32Bit
Grrrrr! It erased my desktop icons and deleted my start-up programs. Be careful on how to use this. If you're happy with your computer set up, let it be.
